Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.56,0:09:46.52,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}确认机械臂动作
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.52,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}还剩3米
