Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.83,0:10:01.95,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}开始锁紧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.46,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}实验船 成功锁紧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.93,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}成功停靠
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.93,0:10:20.93,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}盾状面板一切正常 气压正常
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.05,0:10:24.89,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}舱门可开启 欢迎来到宇宙站
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.35,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}贵国送来了人偶呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.77,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}去给它们打声招呼吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.53,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}假人去哪了？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.33,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}怎么回事？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.54,0:10:55.80,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}为什么不是假人 反而是两个孩子？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.43,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}我们有炸弹
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}但我们想和平解决问题
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.81,0:11:09.94,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}都退后吧 让我们好好谈谈
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.94,0:11:12.35,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}这里有点窄
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.48,0:11:15.07,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}去宽敞点的地方谈吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.19,0:11:17.11,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}快 后退
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.82,0:11:22.82,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}所以
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.82,0:11:26.95,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}请把研究资料拷贝一份给我们
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.04,0:11:30.00,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}我们只有这个要求
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.50,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}我想你们也知道
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.96,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}我们班主任是个怪物
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.08,0:11:39.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}你们要是不配合 我可不知道它会在地球上做出什么事来
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.32,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}因为
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.87,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}我们每天都面临着发生爆炸的危险
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.99,0:12:11.16,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}我们就是这样豁出命在做实验
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.83,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}太鲁莽了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.62,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}准备好资料
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.56,0:15:17.27,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}你们是了不起的勇士
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.43,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}欢迎再来玩
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.56,0:15:20.27,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}但下次要走正规流程
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.81,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}我可不想再来了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.44,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}但要是我成了大人物
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.57,0:15:28.49,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}我会增加宇宙开发预算的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.49,0:15:31.16,TEXT-CN,,0,0,5,,{\fn【暖色君】洛竹体\b0\bord0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs80\fsp0\shad3\4a&H4B&\1a&H14&}好 我等着呢
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.28,0:22:59.61,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an1}我要把寒假的遗憾一口气补救回来
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.96,0:23:00.45,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an3}他肯定能做出决定
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.98,0:23:02.08,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an1}这番话让我第一次意识到
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.56,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an3}那家伙疯得也太可怕了
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.94,0:23:05.88,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fscx90}那我究竟该以怎样的表情 怎样的话语送给他呢
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.99,0:23:07.72,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fscx90}她这一点还真像雪村老师
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.57,0:23:08.98,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an1}那家伙很自卑
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.07,0:23:10.95,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,我会用最灿烂的笑容去支持他
